						<div class="postbody">The motor is definitely disabled when you press the eject button, as nothing prevents you to do that during a load for example.
<br />
<br />This is probably one of the only ways to have the reading head rest "in the middle of nowhere" instead of being at it's rest position at the end of the disc.</div>

					
